acceptance_criteria: "pm comments accepts positional and --add shorthand, plus --stdin and --file for multiline markdown; conflicting input sources error deterministically; contracts/completion/Pi/docs/tests updated and passing."
definition_of_ready: Epic accepted and command/test surfaces for comments are identified.
order: 1
goal: Agent-first CLI ergonomics
objective: Ship intuitive comments invocation
value: Removes a high-frequency agent failure mode
impact: Higher mutation success rate in automation flows
outcome: Comments command accepts intuitive shorthand and remains backward compatible
why_now: Current UX causes frequent too-many-arguments errors
reviewer: maintainer-review
risk: low
confidence: high
